OL,4,Csince pandemic as thousands taken each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FExclusive figures obtained by ITV
OL,8,FCymru Wales have shown the true extent
OL,9,Fof car crime in Wales, with nearly
OL,10,Ffour thousand vehicles stolen across
OL,11,Fthe country in 2024 alone.
OL,13,FOne victim has said she was struggling
OL,14,Fto sleep at night while another said
OL,15,Fshe worried about taking her ill son
OL,16,Fto medical appointments after their
OL,17,Fcars were stolen in what they believe
OL,18,Fwere targeted incidents.
