OL,7,FHelen Crabb and Bridie (who asked for
OL,8,Fher surname not to be shared) have
OL,9,Fdetailed the emotional impact of
OL,10,Fhaving both of their vehicles stolen
OL,11,Fin November 2024.
OL,13,FA freedom of information request
OL,14,Fshowed that over the last 5 years, car
OL,15,Ftheft in Wales has risen by more than
OL,16,F30 percent.
