OL,7,FThe only Welsh police force to see a
OL,8,Fdrop in car crime in this time was
OL,9,FNorth Wales Police, but despite this
OL,10,Falmost 400 were stolen in the area
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FAdrian and Helen Crabb installed
OL,14,Fadditional security measures on their
OL,15,Fhome in November after thieves
OL,16,Finitially tried to take their vehicle,
OL,17,Fthe perpetrators were still able to
OL,18,Freturn a week later and steal it.
