OL,7,FThe pair from Penrhiwfer near
OL,8,FTonyrefail said they feel cheated and
OL,9,Ftargeted by the incident:
OL,11,F"I knew they would come back. We
OL,12,Fdidn't know if they were targeting us
OL,13,Fas a household as the car," said Helen.
OL,15,F"I wasn't sleeping, I was waiting for
OL,16,Fthem to come back, I didn't know what
OL,17,Fwe could do to stop them. I just kept
OL,18,Fthinking 'they're not going to get my
OL,19,Fcar'."
