OL,8,Fvehicle was missing from where she had
OL,9,Fparked it nearby her property.
OL,11,F"I thought the car's not there and I
OL,12,Fwent half way down the steps and
OL,13,Fthought I must have parked it further
OL,14,Fup so half of my mind is saying the
OL,15,Fcars gone the other half is saying
OL,16,Fdon't be silly it's still there.
