OL,7,F"So I went all the way down to the
OL,8,Fpavement and the spaces where my car
OL,9,Fwas, was empty and I just remember
OL,10,Fstanding in the middle of the street
OL,11,Fgoing they've got my car, they took my
OL,12,Fcar."
OL,14,FThe pair's car was found two weeks
OL,15,Flater by police, with its number
OL,16,Fplates changed and evidence that
OL,17,Fsomeone else had been using it.
OL,19,FThey say they believe they were
