OL,7,FChief Inspector Andrew Boucher from
OL,8,Fthe force said that the primary issue
OL,9,Fthey are facing relating to vehicle
OL,10,Fcrime is key-less entry vehicle theft.
OL,12,F"Criminals are able to exploit
OL,13,Fvulnerabilities in key-less entry
OL,14,Ftechnology by using remote devices to
OL,15,Fessentially relay the signal from your
OL,16,Fvehicle keys to the car essentially
OL,17,Ffooling the vehicle into thinking the
OL,18,Fperson has got the keys.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/19
