OL,7,F"There are ways that people can
OL,8,Fprotect themselves, the most simple is
OL,9,Fusing a faraday pouch. The pouch will
OL,10,Fblock your keys from producing the
OL,11,Fsignal and prevent the prospective
OL,12,Fthieves from being able to take the
OL,13,Fvehicle in the future.
OL,15,F"Probably the most reliable form of
OL,16,Fvehicle safety technology is the old
OL,17,Ffashioned stuff like the steering
OL,18,Fwheel lock, the handbrake lock, which
OL,19,Fis tech proof."
